# SOCIALCLUB::SC_TRANSITION_NEWS_HAS_EXTRA_DATA_TU

## Summary
Find whether the currently displayed news item contains extra data

## Returns
* **BOOL**:
True if the there is a news item currently being shown and it contains extra data.
Otherwise false.
